    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Bowls intended primarily for serving an individual portion of soup; made with or without handles and sometimes accompanied by a saucer or cover or both.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
